<varlistentry id="options.Angle">
	<term>Angle</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Defines angle on the hue circle between Inactive1, Base and Inactive2 colors in color schemes, that are automagically calculated by AfterStep.
Default angle is 30 degrees. Use smaller angle to make Inactive and Base colors more similar.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
